sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant WK as Worker
  participant DB as MongoDB
  participant E as OpenAI Embeddings
  participant M as Model

  WK->>DB: list ended conversations in the period
  WK->>WK: extract representative question per convo (heuristic, no model)
  WK->>E: batch-embed questions
  E-->>WK: vectors
  WK->>WK: cluster_by_similarity (cosine graph, in-memory)
  loop each notable cluster (>= size 3)
    WK->>M: classify → theme label · coverage · proposed FAQ
    opt daily run + coverage missing/unclear
      WK->>DB: audit propose_faq → upsert canonical DRAFT (insight_ intent)
    end
  end
  WK->>M: classify → insights narrative
  WK->>DB: upsert insights_report (idempotent per "<type>:<key>")
